title: [1508521049] Best British Restaurant: The Milestone - Gordon Ramsay
description:
Gordon Ramsay goes in search of Britain's best restaurant. Top restaurants from around the UK compete to win the title. 

In this clip Gordon visits Sheffield restaurant The Milestone.
